{"tid":1423660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英仙座流星雨 8月係高峰期","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:43:46.000Z","uid":121030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63704bc463a5143fc0259476b924b7f9b8279004","tid":1423660,"uid":121030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"新月發生在7月31日的夜晚，所以會不斷地變亮。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最佳時候將是8月9日之後</span>，因為流星的頻率愈高，也代表着愈接近峰值。若是看到的話一定不要把目光移開，你可能會錯過，流星動作很很快。英仙座可以大約每秒60公里的速度飛過。<br />\n<br />\n8月9日，木星和月亮將在南方天空中貼的非常近，對於夜空觀星有小小福利，亦是英仙座流星雨的高峰期。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊買觀星筆同望遠鏡觀星喇！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20190804/tbc1_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTor%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20190804%2Ftbc1_r.htm&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=8a298f07\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20190804/tbc1_r.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f0ad4c1266439bf7b7a0dc923778a7715e56c9a8","tid":1423660,"uid":121030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"612ff536d2439e83e8572f848d32e5898df23621","tid":1423660,"uid":121030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3149dfc4e12fe459fa6189fd9cf9ea8241cc7c84","tid":1423660,"uid":121030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef16afbb2ac20dcc184f595f5f1541cd964a7933","tid":1423660,"uid":121030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊觀星！"},{"pid":"c448bd6f5b151fd5b584b7ca3b3e362d716e45cd","tid":1423660,"uid":121030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"推到有人一齊觀星"},{"pid":"d2c577c03080f78be8980964db167a210ab7d72d","tid":1423660,"uid":121030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":